WEBVTT

01:52.500 --> 01:57.380
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.400 --> 02:01.810
[Episode 22]

02:04.430 --> 02:06.180
So you mean...

02:06.210 --> 02:08.870
our current research plan
needs to be scrapped?

02:10.470 --> 02:11.750
The letter indicates

02:11.750 --> 02:14.190
that after Tian Xing
went to Yong City this time,

02:14.190 --> 02:15.850
he found that the people there

02:16.270 --> 02:19.470
were drinking the Spirit Immortal Water
laced with alum.

02:19.470 --> 02:21.910
And when he had abdominal pain
and diarrhea as a child,

02:21.910 --> 02:23.970
his sister would give him alum water,

02:24.270 --> 02:26.200
saying it could stop the diarrhea.

02:27.100 --> 02:28.240
That is to say,

02:28.710 --> 02:29.770
the symptoms like

02:29.910 --> 02:31.750
fever and fatigue in the patients

02:31.750 --> 02:34.550
were a series of reactions
caused by the diarrhea.

02:34.620 --> 02:35.710
So the diarrhea

02:36.100 --> 02:38.150
is the main symptom this time.

02:40.060 --> 02:40.780
Besides,

02:41.150 --> 02:43.100
the samples brought back previously

02:43.100 --> 02:45.380
had traces of being gnawed by rats.

02:46.100 --> 02:47.220
So we have been

02:47.590 --> 02:49.540
focusing our investigation

02:49.540 --> 02:50.540
on the plague.

02:51.780 --> 02:54.470
Taking all the previous circumstances
into account,

02:54.470 --> 02:55.270
this epidemic

02:55.750 --> 02:57.470
is a severe malaria outbreak

02:58.150 --> 02:59.610
caused by mosquito bites.

03:02.150 --> 03:03.590
This epidemic

03:04.220 --> 03:05.910
is recorded in the books.

03:06.820 --> 03:08.020
I remember

03:08.870 --> 03:10.330
there are roughly 4 types:

03:10.340 --> 03:12.060
first, toxic miasma from mountain streams;

03:12.060 --> 03:13.590
second, wind-heat phlegm;

03:14.060 --> 03:15.710
third, pathogenic factors;

03:16.340 --> 03:17.590
fourth, heat toxin.

03:18.190 --> 03:19.579
And among these four,

03:19.820 --> 03:20.880
the most severe one

03:21.030 --> 03:21.900
is heat toxin.

03:22.270 --> 03:23.170
So I suspect

03:23.620 --> 03:24.480
that this time,

03:25.060 --> 03:26.260
it should be malaria.

03:27.590 --> 03:28.390
That's right.

03:28.820 --> 03:30.150
And it spread so rapidly

03:30.410 --> 03:32.870
that it became overwhelming
in a short time.

03:37.360 --> 03:38.360
Your Excellency,

03:38.430 --> 03:39.920
we can handle it.

03:41.750 --> 03:42.540
But...

03:42.780 --> 03:44.840
you have to help me deal with someone.

03:46.310 --> 03:47.780
Lord Jiang's collection of books

03:47.780 --> 03:49.440
is indeed as vast as the ocean.

03:50.030 --> 03:51.710
Tian Xing wasn't exaggerating

03:51.710 --> 03:53.640
when he said he couldn't move them.

03:54.260 --> 03:55.260
Your Excellency?

03:55.620 --> 03:56.660
Why are you here?

03:57.940 --> 03:59.060
I was afraid you'd be tired,

03:59.060 --> 04:00.190
so I came to help you.

04:01.220 --> 04:01.850
Okay,

04:01.870 --> 04:03.070
let's look together.

05:56.780 --> 05:58.630
Why can't we find it?

06:00.130 --> 06:02.060
We've looked everywhere I should.

06:05.860 --> 06:08.120
I don't think I've seen this book before.

06:10.860 --> 06:11.940
This is...

07:57.150 --> 07:58.950
Your Excellency, you're awake?

07:59.030 --> 08:00.680
I... I think I found it.

08:00.980 --> 08:01.830
Look.

08:02.590 --> 08:04.320
Sweet wormwood prescription.

08:04.520 --> 08:05.980
It's the sweet wormwood prescription.

08:05.980 --> 08:07.740
I found it.

08:10.180 --> 08:11.030
You found it?

08:12.300 --> 08:14.150
Wei Ying, hurry!

08:15.870 --> 08:16.870
Your Excellency!

08:17.360 --> 08:18.760
-They found it?
-Fan Yun?

08:20.510 --> 08:21.450
We found it.

08:21.620 --> 08:22.930
It's the sweet wormwood prescription.

08:22.930 --> 08:24.460
It's recorded in this book.

08:24.960 --> 08:26.230
It says,

08:26.340 --> 08:27.470
sweet wormwood...

08:28.100 --> 08:29.030
Take...

08:29.420 --> 08:30.830
2 liters of something...

08:31.470 --> 08:32.480
Wring it out,

08:32.650 --> 08:33.850
and then drink it all.

08:34.230 --> 08:34.940
Look.

08:39.659 --> 08:40.659
This ancient book

08:41.150 --> 08:42.340
is incomplete

08:42.630 --> 08:43.750
and blurry.

08:43.990 --> 08:45.940
As for what the 2 liters refers to

08:45.940 --> 08:47.060
and how it should be wrung out,

08:47.060 --> 08:48.110
it's not clear.

08:49.390 --> 08:50.610
However,

08:50.820 --> 08:52.140
we can look throug

08:52.230 --> 08:54.090
more medical books for reference

08:54.630 --> 08:55.910
and see if we can reconstruct

08:55.910 --> 08:57.760
the original text of this ancient book

08:57.760 --> 08:59.330
and find the right way
to test the medicine.

08:59.330 --> 09:00.300
Then let's not delay.

09:00.300 --> 09:01.540
Wei and Yan, gather all the physicians

09:01.540 --> 09:02.770
in Qi Residence as soon as possible

09:02.770 --> 09:03.910
to work on this prescription together.

09:03.910 --> 09:04.750
-Yes.
-Yes.

09:05.750 --> 09:06.350
Alright.

09:06.350 --> 09:07.350
I'll go with them.

09:10.660 --> 09:12.590
You didn't sleep a wink last night.

09:13.350 --> 09:14.850
Why don't you go back and rest first?

09:14.850 --> 09:16.510
Leave the prescription to me.

09:16.540 --> 09:17.900
No need, Your Excellency.

09:17.900 --> 09:18.700
I'm not tired,

09:18.700 --> 09:20.110
and I don't feel like resting.

09:20.110 --> 09:21.780
I just want to find the prescription
as soon as possible

09:21.780 --> 09:23.510
so that more patients can be treated.

09:23.510 --> 09:24.270
I'll go now.

09:33.700 --> 09:35.230
How is it, Sirs?

09:35.660 --> 09:36.710
How do we prepare this prescription?

09:36.710 --> 09:37.680
Traditional Chinese medicine

09:37.680 --> 09:38.490
is usually

09:38.510 --> 09:39.990
boiled in water.

09:39.990 --> 09:41.700
However, this book

09:41.700 --> 09:43.210
says to wring the herb out.

09:43.450 --> 09:44.840
It should be a special method

09:44.840 --> 09:46.780
used to avoid
destroying certain components

09:46.780 --> 09:49.060
in the sweet wormwood.

09:49.780 --> 09:50.660
That makes sense.

09:50.660 --> 09:53.040
Handbook of Prescriptions for Emergencies
indeed records that sweet wormwood

09:53.040 --> 09:56.170
can clear heat, cool the blood,
and relieve summer heat.

09:56.460 --> 10:00.420
It can also be used to reduce fever
caused by yin deficiency and hot flashes.

10:00.420 --> 10:01.350
However,

10:01.350 --> 10:02.750
there are only ancient records

10:02.750 --> 10:04.480
and no prescriptions or cases.

10:04.870 --> 10:05.910
Nowadays,

10:05.910 --> 10:08.070
malaria in Yong City is so severe.

10:08.390 --> 10:10.110
Simple preparation methods

10:10.870 --> 10:11.930
might not

10:12.300 --> 10:14.360
bring out its medicinal properties.

10:14.510 --> 10:15.700
-Right.
-Right.

10:16.370 --> 10:17.710
So,

10:18.420 --> 10:19.940
we can handle the 2 liters mentioned here

10:19.940 --> 10:21.390
according to this idea

10:21.820 --> 10:23.110
by choosing some medicinal herbs

10:23.110 --> 10:24.500
with strong effects

10:24.660 --> 10:26.150
to mix with sweet wormwood.

10:26.150 --> 10:26.990
That's right.

10:27.660 --> 10:29.400
I heard

10:29.870 --> 10:32.200
that some special components in this herb

10:32.300 --> 10:34.420
can only be activated

10:34.420 --> 10:35.750
by strong stimulation.

10:35.940 --> 10:37.700
As they say, fight poison with poison

10:37.700 --> 10:39.660
to cure the disease.

10:39.840 --> 10:41.460
Then what kind of poison should we use

10:41.460 --> 10:42.820
to mix with it?

10:42.820 --> 10:43.990
Yes.

10:43.990 --> 10:44.750
Well...

10:44.750 --> 10:45.910
Gelsemium elegans,

10:46.420 --> 10:47.580
oleander,

10:47.910 --> 10:48.840
poisonous wine,

10:49.380 --> 10:50.450
and datura

10:50.480 --> 10:51.440
are all options.

10:54.150 --> 10:54.990
Then let's

10:56.060 --> 10:57.300
try them one by one.

11:01.090 --> 11:03.740
♪ Our hearts reach for the morning glow ♪

11:03.910 --> 11:07.370
♪ Our dreams fear no barren land below ♪

11:08.020 --> 11:13.110
♪ What does it matter
if we fly against the wind? ♪

11:13.550 --> 11:16.130
♪ We vow to live up
to our youthful prime ♪

11:16.390 --> 11:20.200
♪ To walk alongside ordinary folks alike ♪

11:20.770 --> 11:23.700
♪ Sharing the same ray of light ♪

11:23.870 --> 11:29.400
♪ Fear no strange land nor dim twilight ♪

11:28.940 --> 11:30.460
Turn down the heat.

11:29.580 --> 11:32.650
♪ All for this boundless world ♪

11:30.460 --> 11:31.820
It's almost done.

11:32.670 --> 11:37.780
♪ To wear a robe of radiant glory ♪

11:36.230 --> 11:37.270
Your Excellency,

11:37.270 --> 11:38.750
it's about time.

11:38.750 --> 11:40.030
Bring them all out then.

11:39.180 --> 11:44.770
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

11:44.960 --> 11:49.150
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

11:48.510 --> 11:49.630
Physician Li,

11:49.180 --> 11:51.310
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

11:49.630 --> 11:51.150
are the antidotes all prepared,

11:51.150 --> 11:53.030
and are you sure everyone will be safe?

11:51.510 --> 11:57.200
♪ Chase the light,
let our dreams unfold wide ♪

11:53.030 --> 11:53.870
Yes.

11:53.870 --> 11:55.350
Rest assured, Your Excellency.

11:55.350 --> 11:56.910
Taken in moderation,

11:56.910 --> 11:58.060
this medicine poses no threat to life.

11:57.320 --> 12:01.540
♪ With bold resolve, ignite plain faith ♪

11:58.910 --> 11:59.780
That's good.

12:00.540 --> 12:01.570
Thank you all for your trouble.

12:01.570 --> 12:03.430
♪ Light them up ♪

12:03.460 --> 12:07.190
♪ Let all wind and frost of days gone by ♪

12:07.330 --> 12:13.400
♪ Turn to countless beams
of light within my eye ♪

12:13.430 --> 12:19.690
♪ Await the sight of you ♪

12:16.780 --> 12:17.900
Physicians,

12:17.920 --> 12:18.640
how is it?

12:20.270 --> 12:22.070
This prescription is not right.

12:23.690 --> 12:24.520
Physician Li,

12:24.580 --> 12:25.580
what about yours?

12:26.030 --> 12:27.150
Not this one either.

12:27.150 --> 12:28.110
Physicians,

12:28.110 --> 12:29.110
what about yours?

12:29.740 --> 12:30.780
Not this one.

12:33.230 --> 12:33.940
My Lord,

12:34.230 --> 12:35.870
the pulse has changed.
It's this prescription.

12:35.870 --> 12:36.460
Fan Yun!

12:37.390 --> 12:38.390
Your Excellency!

12:39.260 --> 12:40.910
That's wonderful, Your Excellency!

12:40.910 --> 12:42.220
We found the medicine!

12:42.870 --> 12:43.780
-Well...
-Great!

12:43.780 --> 12:45.060
does this mean Yong City is saved?

12:45.060 --> 12:45.750
Yes!

12:45.800 --> 12:46.770
Yong City is saved!

12:46.770 --> 12:48.730
-We did it!
-That's great!

12:49.180 --> 12:50.460
We finally found it!

12:50.460 --> 12:51.300
Next,

12:51.590 --> 12:53.810
we just need
to gather the medicinal herbs.

12:53.810 --> 12:56.780
[Juyun Pavilion]

13:10.110 --> 13:10.730
Boss,

13:10.970 --> 13:12.830
Lady Fan Yun went to the herb firm.

13:14.420 --> 13:15.230
What?

13:16.460 --> 13:18.140
Juyun Pavilion has everything.

13:18.140 --> 13:19.800
Why did she go to the herb firm?

13:21.030 --> 13:22.030
What do you think?

13:24.940 --> 13:26.760
Those misers at the herb firm.

13:27.110 --> 13:29.150
I went to negotiate a deal with them
several times,

13:29.150 --> 13:30.950
but we couldn't agree on a price.

13:31.390 --> 13:33.990
The price you offered
indeed wasn't very high.

13:36.230 --> 13:37.150
But...

13:37.700 --> 13:38.990
it was very fair.

13:38.990 --> 13:39.970
They are just too greedy.

13:39.970 --> 13:40.830
It's a rip-off.

13:41.230 --> 13:42.360
I can't go this time.

13:42.780 --> 13:43.420
I got it.

13:45.700 --> 13:46.350
Wait.

13:50.420 --> 13:51.880
I'll go take a look anyway.

13:52.390 --> 13:54.850
Then I will leave this matter to you,
Mr. Cao.

13:55.060 --> 13:55.990
You're welcome.

13:56.540 --> 13:57.780
Tomorrow I'll send someone

13:57.780 --> 13:59.510
to deliver the herbs to you.

14:00.560 --> 14:01.630
Thank you, Mr. Cao.

14:01.700 --> 14:02.700
Don't mention it.

14:03.180 --> 14:04.960
Making the best use of herbs

14:05.150 --> 14:06.750
is what our firm is all about.

14:07.420 --> 14:09.680
Now that you need them to save lives,

14:09.990 --> 14:11.650
we are naturally duty-bound.

14:13.390 --> 14:15.390
You can take my carriage back first.

14:19.320 --> 14:20.470
I knew it.

14:21.300 --> 14:22.110
Fan Yun!

14:25.060 --> 14:26.060
Why is he here again?

14:26.060 --> 14:26.660
Zheng...

14:32.560 --> 14:33.560
Young Master Lou.

14:33.580 --> 14:34.630
Why are you here?

14:35.820 --> 14:37.950
Is he making things difficult for you?

14:38.150 --> 14:39.460
Making things difficult?

14:39.460 --> 14:40.620
Why would he do that?

14:41.700 --> 14:43.150
I told you that whatever you want to do,

14:43.150 --> 14:44.550
I can help you achieve it.

14:47.780 --> 14:48.720
Mr. Cao,

14:49.090 --> 14:50.310
please hand over everything

14:50.310 --> 14:51.640
that Lady Fan Yun needs.

14:53.230 --> 14:55.060
And if I don't do as you say?

14:56.150 --> 14:57.900
Then I'll buy this firm

14:58.170 --> 15:00.170
at the price you previously stated.

15:13.230 --> 15:14.180
Lady Fan Yun,

15:14.750 --> 15:15.680
I didn't expect

15:15.980 --> 15:17.510
you and Juyun Pavilion

15:18.030 --> 15:19.150
to be so close.

15:20.390 --> 15:21.230
I...

15:22.540 --> 15:24.300
I didn't expect it either.

15:25.820 --> 15:27.280
Then I've changed my mind.

15:27.540 --> 15:30.070
I can't give you the sweet wormwood
so easily.

15:33.620 --> 15:34.380
You...

15:44.600 --> 15:46.320
I am Fan Yun, a newly appointed official.

15:46.320 --> 15:48.270
I am here about the Yong City plague.

15:48.270 --> 15:49.730
I ask for your assistance.

15:50.700 --> 15:51.360
Lady Fan Yun

15:51.360 --> 15:52.920
needs our sweet wormwood

15:53.210 --> 15:55.110
to make a specific medicine
for the plague,

15:55.110 --> 15:56.440
and the more the better.

15:56.580 --> 15:57.820
As for this matter,

15:57.820 --> 16:00.150
I originally wanted to make the decision.

16:00.390 --> 16:03.580
But the arrival of Young Master Lou Qiyan
of Juyun Pavilion

16:03.580 --> 16:05.110
reminded me of something.

16:07.420 --> 16:08.290
What is it?

16:10.180 --> 16:11.510
The biggest difference

16:11.700 --> 16:13.970
between our trade and Juyun Pavilion

16:14.230 --> 16:16.540
is that we operate through consultation
and shared governance.

16:16.540 --> 16:18.990
We are not a one-man operation
backed by sheer wealth.

16:18.990 --> 16:20.660
So for this matter,

16:20.660 --> 16:22.720
besides persuading me, Lady Fan Yun,

16:22.940 --> 16:24.870
you also need to persuade everyone here.

16:24.870 --> 16:27.600
Sweet wormwood
is a good medicine for the plague?

16:28.150 --> 16:28.750
Yes.

16:29.270 --> 16:31.270
We have developed all the formulas.

16:31.420 --> 16:32.520
However,

16:32.750 --> 16:34.510
Qi Residence has limited raw materials.

16:34.510 --> 16:35.510
That is why I came here

16:35.510 --> 16:36.870
to ask for your help.

16:36.870 --> 16:39.060
This is a good thing that benefits
both the people and ourselves.

16:39.060 --> 16:41.120
We are naturally duty-bound to help.

16:41.300 --> 16:42.580
But I heard

16:42.580 --> 16:45.540
that the Yong City plague is contagious.

16:45.540 --> 16:46.950
Yeah.

16:47.390 --> 16:49.350
You just need
to hand over the sweet wormwood.

16:49.350 --> 16:51.660
Juyun Pavilion
will handle the transportation.

16:51.660 --> 16:53.230
No disease will infect you.

16:54.910 --> 16:56.150
Actually, this disease

16:56.150 --> 16:58.300
does not spread from person to person.

16:58.700 --> 17:00.700
As long as we take
good mosquito protection measures,

17:00.700 --> 17:02.320
there will be no danger.

17:02.580 --> 17:03.590
Since it's safe,

17:03.820 --> 17:05.020
-then we...
-Well...

17:05.980 --> 17:08.150
This is a considerable expense.

17:08.150 --> 17:10.790
I wonder if Qi Residence
has allocated special funds

17:10.790 --> 17:13.390
to cover the costs
of our manpower and resources.

17:13.390 --> 17:16.390
Didn't you see those boxes at the door?

17:19.700 --> 17:21.560
We don't want to get involved with

17:21.690 --> 17:23.089
Juyun Pavilion too much.

17:25.310 --> 17:26.710
Regarding the expenses,

17:26.940 --> 17:28.740
I have an unreasonable request.

17:30.390 --> 17:31.770
I wonder if you

17:31.980 --> 17:33.180
recognize this book.

17:33.460 --> 17:34.550
This book is...

17:34.830 --> 17:36.310
-Isn't this...
-Exactly.

17:36.980 --> 17:39.420
This is an ancient medical book I found

17:39.420 --> 17:40.980
in Lord Jiang's library.

17:40.980 --> 17:42.830
There are also many annotations

17:42.830 --> 17:44.390
made by Lord Jiang himself.

17:44.390 --> 17:46.110
And medical books like this

17:46.110 --> 17:47.830
are countless

17:47.830 --> 17:49.110
in Lord Jiang's home.

17:52.180 --> 17:53.070
Sirs,

17:53.420 --> 17:56.250
as the top herbal medicine experts
across the Nine Cities,

17:56.250 --> 17:57.690
I believe you understand

17:57.720 --> 17:59.740
the commercial value
of these medical books

17:59.740 --> 18:00.470
better

18:00.740 --> 18:02.590
than I do.

18:02.590 --> 18:03.590
Lady Fan Yun,

18:03.940 --> 18:05.830
are you trying to pay us

18:05.830 --> 18:07.160
with this medical book?

18:09.110 --> 18:10.110
Not exactly.

18:10.110 --> 18:11.220
After all, these books

18:11.220 --> 18:13.020
are Lord Jiang's private property.

18:13.020 --> 18:14.590
I cannot use someone else's property
for my own benefit.

18:14.590 --> 18:15.940
Then what do you mean?

18:16.790 --> 18:17.870
You can't

18:17.870 --> 18:20.220
just let us feast our eyes on it, can you?

18:22.590 --> 18:26.450
Lord Jiang is the assistant official
for the Yong City plague this time.

18:26.450 --> 18:27.390
He said that

18:27.390 --> 18:29.660
anyone who helps with this matter

18:29.660 --> 18:31.260
can be considered an advisor.

18:31.260 --> 18:32.060
By then,

18:32.060 --> 18:34.420
you can go to his library

18:34.500 --> 18:35.900
and borrow books at will.

18:43.830 --> 18:45.290
There is such a good thing?

18:45.630 --> 18:48.220
However, Lord Jiang also said

18:48.220 --> 18:49.830
these books can only be borrowed,

18:49.830 --> 18:50.790
not taken away.

18:50.790 --> 18:51.810
So gentlemen,

18:52.070 --> 18:53.700
you still need
to rely on your own abilities

18:53.700 --> 18:54.740
to memorize them.

18:56.420 --> 18:58.220
My Juyun Pavilion has many talents.

18:58.220 --> 19:00.080
This little advantage is enough.

19:06.630 --> 19:07.630
Young Master Lou,

19:08.150 --> 19:09.460
are you trying to compete

19:09.460 --> 19:11.310
for this matter as well?

19:11.310 --> 19:12.110
Yes.

19:12.550 --> 19:14.010
I did a rough calculation.

19:14.070 --> 19:15.550
With Lord Jiang's medical books,

19:15.550 --> 19:16.460
my Juyun Pavilion can develop

19:16.460 --> 19:18.330
countless superior medicines.

19:18.660 --> 19:19.550
When that time comes,

19:19.550 --> 19:21.310
I won't even need to buy this firm.

19:21.310 --> 19:22.770
I'll just open one myself.

19:25.150 --> 19:25.950
This won't do.

19:26.460 --> 19:27.910
But this matter

19:28.150 --> 19:30.260
is related to herbs after all.

19:30.260 --> 19:31.150
I think

19:31.150 --> 19:33.070
these gentlemen are more suitable.

19:33.070 --> 19:35.070
Yes, yes, we are more suitable.

19:35.310 --> 19:35.870
Alright.

19:37.220 --> 19:38.260
That makes sense.

19:38.260 --> 19:40.260
Since we are the most professional,

19:40.260 --> 19:42.390
why let it pass through others' hands?

19:42.910 --> 19:43.610
I'll sign.

19:43.790 --> 19:45.310
- I'll sign!
- I'll sign too!

19:45.310 --> 19:46.790
We all sign!

19:47.790 --> 19:48.500
Okay.

19:48.870 --> 19:51.260
Those who are willing
to participate in this,

19:51.260 --> 19:53.110
come over and sign your names.

19:53.110 --> 19:54.310
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

19:58.470 --> 19:59.100
How was it?

20:00.390 --> 20:01.500
How was what?

20:03.130 --> 20:05.160
I used to disdain helping others.

20:05.630 --> 20:09.230
When I saw people being vulnerable,
I even wanted to step on them.

20:09.630 --> 20:11.150
But today,

20:11.150 --> 20:12.810
you've already stepped on me.

20:22.590 --> 20:24.520
Has the girl from the Fan family

20:24.870 --> 20:27.110
made any moves these days?

20:29.790 --> 20:31.210
Wei Sui sent word

20:31.660 --> 20:34.260
that she had found the herb firm to help.

20:34.260 --> 20:34.980
Right now,

20:34.980 --> 20:37.580
the herbs
are already on their way to Yong City.

20:39.390 --> 20:40.860
They found the herbs?

20:41.110 --> 20:41.930
Yes.

20:42.420 --> 20:43.350
It seems

20:43.350 --> 20:44.630
to be sweet wormwood.

21:22.180 --> 21:23.500
Who are you?

21:23.740 --> 21:25.630
Do you know these
are Juyun Pavilion's carts?

21:25.630 --> 21:26.790
You're exactly who we're here to rob!

21:26.790 --> 21:27.390
Kill them!

21:33.700 --> 21:34.420
Your Excellency?

21:34.420 --> 21:34.910
Fan Yun!

21:34.910 --> 21:35.940
Why are you here?

21:37.390 --> 21:38.390
Did you sleep well?

21:38.390 --> 21:39.660
Why are you here too?

21:40.630 --> 21:42.460
Did you two come together?

21:42.460 --> 21:43.700
-Of course not.
-Of course not.

21:43.700 --> 21:44.870
I came to see you.

21:45.400 --> 21:46.560
I came looking for you.

21:46.560 --> 21:47.320
Fan Yun,

21:47.350 --> 21:48.400
something happened.

21:48.400 --> 21:49.790
The sweet wormwood was stolen.

21:49.790 --> 21:51.520
The sweet wormwood was stolen?

21:51.830 --> 21:54.090
Can you not interrupt when I'm speaking?

21:54.210 --> 21:55.700
It was Juyun Pavilion's convoy.

21:55.700 --> 21:56.790
On the way to Yong City,

21:56.790 --> 21:58.070
they were robbed by bandits.

21:58.070 --> 21:59.220
Bandits?

21:59.910 --> 22:01.180
But why would bandits

22:01.180 --> 22:02.670
rob sweet wormwood?

22:02.910 --> 22:03.910
So I was thinking,

22:04.630 --> 22:06.230
maybe they weren't bandits.

22:13.070 --> 22:14.260
So...

22:15.240 --> 22:16.040
Zheng Yuan!

22:16.060 --> 22:18.500
-Lord Lyu! Lord Lyu!
-Zheng Yuan!

22:19.910 --> 22:21.420
-Lord Lyu!
-Zheng Yuan!

22:21.420 --> 22:22.460
Lord Lyu!

22:23.460 --> 22:25.500
Our Master is unwell
and hasn't gotten up yet.

22:25.500 --> 22:27.350
Please come back another day.

22:27.390 --> 22:28.950
Tell that to someone else!

22:28.970 --> 22:30.660
Tell him to come out and see me now!

22:30.660 --> 22:31.490
Lord Lyu,

22:31.870 --> 22:33.700
please go back for now.

22:33.700 --> 22:35.880
I will pass this on to Lord Zheng.

22:36.310 --> 22:37.260
No need!

22:39.180 --> 22:40.070
Zheng Yuan!

22:41.180 --> 22:44.430
I never thought
you would dare to do such a thing!

22:44.730 --> 22:47.020
Withholding the sweet wormwood
and delaying the medicine delivery!

22:47.020 --> 22:49.220
You are treating human lives like dirt!

22:49.850 --> 22:52.700
Those are all fresh, living human lives!

22:53.310 --> 22:56.920
They are the people
we defended with our lives!

22:57.350 --> 23:00.390
Yet because of your selfish motives,

23:00.390 --> 23:02.740
you abandoned them all!

23:02.740 --> 23:04.150
You must have lost your mind!

23:04.150 --> 23:05.590
Lord Lyu,

23:05.590 --> 23:07.590
you have misunderstood Lord Zheng.

23:07.940 --> 23:09.740
What is there to misunderstand?

23:11.180 --> 23:11.940
Zheng Yuan!

23:13.020 --> 23:15.070
I don't care what your reasons are.

23:17.110 --> 23:18.940
Having done such a thing,

23:18.940 --> 23:22.940
you are unfit
to be Lord Zheng of the Nine Cities!

23:24.350 --> 23:26.150
You are even less fit...

23:27.740 --> 23:30.660
to be my friend.

23:47.550 --> 23:48.220
Wait.

23:49.020 --> 23:50.620
It still doesn't make sense.

23:57.630 --> 23:58.830
I don't get it either.

23:58.840 --> 23:59.910
What exactly is his purpose

23:59.910 --> 24:01.320
for doing this?

24:05.910 --> 24:07.310
Why are you looking at me?

24:07.870 --> 24:10.070
You and Lord Zheng share a deep
grandparent-grandchild bond,

24:10.070 --> 24:11.590
and you understand each other well.

24:11.590 --> 24:12.460
Share your thoughts.

24:12.460 --> 24:13.220
Yes.

24:13.870 --> 24:15.180
Tell us what you think.

24:16.070 --> 24:18.390
Grandfather has always felt that
Fan Yun is misleading the public,

24:18.390 --> 24:21.130
bewitching the Governor to promote
the national selection exam.

24:21.130 --> 24:22.980
He wants to use this to ruin Fan Yun,

24:22.980 --> 24:24.500
abolish the national selection exam,

24:24.500 --> 24:26.220
and restore things to how they used to be.

24:26.220 --> 24:28.020
I still feel something is wrong.

24:28.070 --> 24:29.940
Gambling with the lives of the people

24:29.940 --> 24:32.470
just to abolish
the national selection exam?

24:33.020 --> 24:35.150
This doesn't seem like something

24:35.180 --> 24:36.530
Lord Zheng would do.

24:38.150 --> 24:40.310
Grandfather's way of doing things
this time

24:40.310 --> 24:41.510
is indeed a bit crazy.

24:41.790 --> 24:42.790
Crazy?

24:43.310 --> 24:44.460
It's simply absurd.

24:45.630 --> 24:46.700
Anyway,

24:47.110 --> 24:48.870
the most important thing right now

24:48.870 --> 24:49.980
is to quickly send the sweet wormwood

24:49.980 --> 24:51.440
to Yong City to save lives.

24:51.590 --> 24:52.630
But...

24:53.460 --> 24:55.420
what is the best way to do it?

25:00.070 --> 25:01.420
Right, Your Excellency.

25:01.420 --> 25:03.180
We can use the beacon tower.

25:03.790 --> 25:04.790
The beacon tower?

25:05.830 --> 25:08.020
When trouble occurs at one spot,
help comes from all quarters.

25:08.020 --> 25:09.150
If we light the beacon tower,

25:09.150 --> 25:11.150
the other 8 cities will

25:11.150 --> 25:12.070
receive the message at top speed.

25:12.070 --> 25:12.940
Then,

25:12.940 --> 25:14.180
they will
send the sweet wormwood over

25:14.180 --> 25:15.310
as fast as possible.

25:20.550 --> 25:22.080
-Let's do it right now.
-No!

25:22.150 --> 25:23.220
Absolutely not!

25:23.410 --> 25:25.260
Have you forgotten
what I promised Lord Zheng?

25:25.260 --> 25:26.790
During the trial period
of the national selection exam,

25:26.790 --> 25:28.020
if the beacon tower is lit,

25:28.020 --> 25:29.830
it means asking for help
from major noble families.

25:29.830 --> 25:30.790
In this way,

25:30.790 --> 25:32.340
the national selection exam
will be abolished immediately.

25:32.340 --> 25:34.200
But if you light the beacon tower,

25:34.460 --> 25:36.150
you won't be able
to keep your official position.

25:36.150 --> 25:36.810
Therefore,

25:37.140 --> 25:38.200
no one can light it.

25:38.420 --> 25:39.390
But...

25:39.740 --> 25:41.870
So this was Grandfather's purpose
all along.

25:41.870 --> 25:44.470
Now all the blame is placed on the reform.

25:47.070 --> 25:48.130
That makes sense.

25:48.790 --> 25:50.520
As expected of my grandfather.

25:53.260 --> 25:54.590
What are you so proud of?

25:55.500 --> 25:57.760
Is craziness hereditary in your family?

25:58.350 --> 26:00.390
Our Zheng family has been brave
and good at fighting since ancient times,

26:00.390 --> 26:01.930
producing generations of talents.

26:01.930 --> 26:04.450
Our Qi family has a majestic aura!

26:06.030 --> 26:07.160
Where are you going?

26:10.180 --> 26:11.310
I'm hungry.

26:11.310 --> 26:13.280
Anyway, our Fan family can't go hungry.

26:13.280 --> 26:16.480
You Qi family and Zheng family
can take your time arguing.

26:20.310 --> 26:21.020
What?

26:24.070 --> 26:25.110
We are hungry too.

26:25.940 --> 26:26.870
Alright.

26:26.870 --> 26:28.700
I'll bring some good food back for you.

26:28.700 --> 26:29.680
Once you're full,

26:29.680 --> 26:31.480
you'll have the energy to argue.

26:37.390 --> 26:38.720
Take your time arguing.

26:42.790 --> 26:43.520
I'm leaving.

26:43.980 --> 26:44.590
Take me with you.

26:44.590 --> 26:45.330
It's not on the way.

26:45.330 --> 26:47.150
I'm not going back to my residence.
It is on the way.

26:47.150 --> 26:48.550
You want to go to my house?

26:49.260 --> 26:50.220
Don't bother.

26:50.220 --> 26:51.980
Grandfather must have expected this.

26:51.980 --> 26:53.370
He won't see anyone,

26:53.500 --> 26:54.430
especially you.

26:54.790 --> 26:56.120
I'm not going to see him.

26:56.420 --> 26:57.820
Then where are you going?

26:59.740 --> 27:00.870
To the beacon tower.

27:01.630 --> 27:03.830
Aren't you afraid of affecting Fan Yun?

27:06.740 --> 27:09.870
Why is it taking Fan Yun so long
to make food and come back?

27:15.220 --> 27:16.020
Fan Yun!

27:17.350 --> 27:18.910
Why did you lock the door?

27:19.070 --> 27:20.780
Don't go to the beacon tower by yourself!

27:20.780 --> 27:22.710
Fan Yun, hurry up and open the door!

27:23.310 --> 27:25.270
Fan Yun's trick
of catching a rat in a trap

27:25.270 --> 27:26.470
is really brilliant.

27:27.910 --> 27:28.980
Are you a rat?

27:30.070 --> 27:31.930
Whoever wants to go out is the rat.

27:32.700 --> 27:34.700
I think staying here is pretty good.

27:37.020 --> 27:37.790
Fan Yun!

27:37.790 --> 27:38.840
Be careful!

27:38.980 --> 27:40.910
I'll be waiting for your good news.

27:41.350 --> 27:43.200
Stop being glib, will you?

27:43.310 --> 27:45.170
Hurry up and help me open the door.

27:47.260 --> 27:48.660
What are you waiting for?

27:49.080 --> 27:50.810
Why should I go against Fan Yun?

27:51.260 --> 27:52.220
What do you mean?

27:53.940 --> 27:56.000
Are you taking Fan Yun's side on this?

27:56.180 --> 27:57.440
Or should I take yours?

27:58.110 --> 27:59.660
Do you know what it means

27:59.660 --> 28:00.550
for Fan Yun to go light the beacon tower?

28:00.550 --> 28:01.100
I do.

28:01.350 --> 28:03.070
It means she is going over
the Governor's authority

28:03.070 --> 28:05.110
to get medicine
for the people of Yong City.

28:05.110 --> 28:06.320
What's wrong with that?

28:06.320 --> 28:08.400
Fan Yun will be impeached
and held accountable,

28:08.400 --> 28:10.630
or even lose her qualification to be an official.
Do you know that?

28:10.630 --> 28:12.700
That's exactly the result I want.

28:12.700 --> 28:13.700
The door of my Juyun Pavilion

28:13.700 --> 28:15.230
will always be open for her.

28:15.630 --> 28:17.070
Do you even know

28:17.550 --> 28:19.180
why Fan Yun divorced me?

28:20.390 --> 28:22.350
Because she didn't want
to live with you anymore.

28:22.350 --> 28:23.660
Then what about her training
at the Commerce Bureau?

28:23.660 --> 28:24.870
Studying day and night,

28:24.870 --> 28:26.110
preparing for the selection exam,

28:26.110 --> 28:27.830
and trying desperately
to pass her internship?

28:27.830 --> 28:30.160
If all she wanted was freedom and leisure,

28:30.260 --> 28:31.110
why did she have to take it step by step,

28:31.110 --> 28:33.260
braving difficulties and dangers
to get here?

28:33.260 --> 28:34.390
Do you think what you can give her

28:34.390 --> 28:35.830
is what she wants?

28:36.350 --> 28:37.700
Does she want what you can give her?

28:37.700 --> 28:38.760
She wants neither!

28:38.940 --> 28:40.670
Neither of us can give it to her!

28:41.420 --> 28:43.280
Only what she strives for herself

28:43.910 --> 28:45.240
is what she truly wants.

28:54.110 --> 28:55.390
That makes some sense,

28:56.020 --> 28:56.830
but not much.

28:57.110 --> 28:58.160
Stop nagging.

28:58.310 --> 29:00.170
Hurry up and help me open the door!

29:14.130 --> 29:15.690
I really can't run anymore!

29:17.590 --> 29:18.350
Fan Yun!

29:19.830 --> 29:20.660
Fan Yun!

29:21.260 --> 29:22.520
Fan Yun, stop running!

29:24.110 --> 29:26.040
Your Excellency, stop chasing me!

29:26.390 --> 29:28.110
If you stop running, I'll stop chasing!

29:28.110 --> 29:30.510
I can only stop running
if you stop chasing!

29:30.920 --> 29:32.050
I'll stop chasing.

29:32.080 --> 29:33.310
So you stop running too.

29:33.310 --> 29:34.060
Okay.

29:34.220 --> 29:35.740
Then stop chasing.

29:37.150 --> 29:38.810
And... and I'll stop running.

29:43.260 --> 29:44.310
You tricked me!

29:44.830 --> 29:45.500
Fan Yun!

30:22.700 --> 30:23.590
Fan Yun!

30:25.500 --> 30:26.390
Fan Yun!

30:30.660 --> 30:31.420
Fan Yun!

30:31.820 --> 30:34.350
Military zone!
No entry for plain commoners!

30:39.530 --> 30:40.260
Fan Yun,

30:40.590 --> 30:41.660
you're overstepping your authority!

30:41.660 --> 30:42.980
I can punish you for this!

30:42.980 --> 30:44.110
Come down right now!

30:44.590 --> 30:45.590
Your Excellency,

30:46.110 --> 30:47.150
we both know

30:48.020 --> 30:49.350
that this is the only way

30:49.830 --> 30:51.110
and the best way.

30:57.800 --> 30:58.760
Then let me

30:58.830 --> 30:59.760
light this fire.

31:00.110 --> 31:00.660
No!

31:02.630 --> 31:03.230
You can't.

31:06.310 --> 31:08.110
For the national selection exam

31:08.260 --> 31:09.860
and to abolish the old rules,

31:10.420 --> 31:12.350
you have lain low for so many years.

31:12.830 --> 31:14.020
And all these years,

31:14.020 --> 31:14.590
you have been pretending to be...

31:14.590 --> 31:15.790
Enough! Say no more!

31:22.630 --> 31:24.030
Fan Yun, I'm telling you.

31:24.500 --> 31:26.180
If you light this fire now,

31:27.310 --> 31:29.240
it will be a crime of overstepping.

31:29.420 --> 31:31.760
Not only will your political career
end again,

31:31.760 --> 31:32.520
I...

31:38.310 --> 31:41.370
I'm just afraid I won't be able
to protect you, you know?

31:55.780 --> 31:56.970
But if you light it,

31:57.260 --> 31:59.660
the political careers of all the commoners

31:59.660 --> 32:00.870
who have already passed the selection exam

32:00.870 --> 32:02.630
will end.

32:07.420 --> 32:08.790
A year ago, I

32:10.420 --> 32:12.680
didn't even have the right to stand here.

32:13.020 --> 32:14.350
But today, I

32:15.550 --> 32:17.220
can use this torch

32:17.220 --> 32:19.460
to save millions of people.

32:22.110 --> 32:24.240
This is what I have always wanted to do,

32:25.070 --> 32:27.270
and the meaning of my being an official.

32:31.390 --> 32:32.390
Your Excellency,

32:32.790 --> 32:33.660
saving Yong City,

32:33.660 --> 32:34.740
reforming the selection exam,

32:34.740 --> 32:36.180
and pacifying the Nine Cities' affairs—

32:36.180 --> 32:37.070
there are so many things

32:37.070 --> 32:38.310
waiting for you to do.

32:39.350 --> 32:41.150
So this fire today

32:41.150 --> 32:42.550
must be lit by me.

32:45.790 --> 32:47.150
Sacrificing one Fan Yun

32:47.940 --> 32:48.940
to save a governor who truly wants

32:48.940 --> 32:50.540
to change the Nine Cities...

32:51.310 --> 32:52.550
I think

32:53.630 --> 32:54.460
it's worth it.

32:59.660 --> 33:05.250
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

33:05.440 --> 33:09.630
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

33:09.660 --> 33:11.790
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

33:11.980 --> 33:17.680
♪ Chase the light,
let our dreams unfold wide ♪

33:17.800 --> 33:22.020
♪ With bold resolve, ignite plain faith ♪

33:22.050 --> 33:23.910
♪ Light them up ♪

33:23.940 --> 33:27.660
♪ Let all wind and frost of days gone by ♪

33:27.800 --> 33:33.880
♪ Turn to countless beams
of light within my eye ♪

33:33.910 --> 33:40.170
♪ Await the sight of you ♪

33:58.070 --> 33:58.980
Fan Yun!

34:04.830 --> 34:06.830
No regrets once the piece is played?

34:09.639 --> 34:10.610
No regrets!

34:14.750 --> 34:15.750
Your Excellency,

34:16.940 --> 34:18.500
being your subject

34:20.020 --> 34:21.270
is my honor.

34:21.350 --> 34:24.110
♪ My heart is unwavering ♪

34:24.600 --> 34:28.110
♪ My dreams become wings ♪

34:28.489 --> 34:32.980
♪ What does it matter
if we fly against the wind? ♪

34:33.860 --> 34:36.750
♪ The most ordinary desire ♪

34:36.780 --> 34:41.400
♪ Is worth lighting up ♪

34:41.420 --> 34:44.050
♪ With my life ♪

34:44.070 --> 34:46.750
♪ From then on ♪

34:46.770 --> 34:49.810
♪ Time left a glimmer of hope ♪

34:50.040 --> 34:58.780
♪ Take it as the glory of my journey ♪

34:59.630 --> 35:05.210
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

35:05.400 --> 35:09.590
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

35:09.620 --> 35:11.750
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

35:11.890 --> 35:17.590
♪ We chase the light and travel together ♪

35:17.800 --> 35:19.780
♪ Not considering how long the road is ♪

35:19.830 --> 35:23.830
♪ When looking back,
I'm still young and stubborn ♪

35:23.850 --> 35:27.600
♪ Let all wind and frost of days gone by ♪

35:27.630 --> 35:30.120
♪ Every place I've been to ♪

35:30.150 --> 35:33.730
♪ Shines brightly ♪

35:33.760 --> 35:38.850
♪ Just as I expected ♪

35:35.390 --> 35:36.310
Master.

35:36.910 --> 35:38.020
The Governor urgently summons

35:38.020 --> 35:41.020
all noble ministers to his mansion
within 15 minutes.

35:43.060 --> 35:45.420
The Governor would give in so easily?

35:46.310 --> 35:49.270
The fire on the beacon tower
wasn't lit by the Governor.

35:49.270 --> 35:50.460
It was Fan Yun.

35:53.940 --> 35:54.920
It was her?

35:57.620 --> 35:59.060
It's not surprising.

35:59.620 --> 36:01.930
It is something she would do.

36:03.580 --> 36:04.500
Master,

36:05.020 --> 36:06.620
can we talk to the Governor tonight

36:06.620 --> 36:08.060
about

36:08.060 --> 36:09.940
impeaching Fan Yun?

36:18.620 --> 36:19.760
Ask for a leave.

36:20.100 --> 36:21.900
You are not going to his mansion?

36:26.350 --> 36:28.350
By order of the Governor!

36:28.350 --> 36:31.980
All Masters must immediately
mobilize their forces

36:31.980 --> 36:35.780
to search for sweet wormwood
in their cities and send it to Yong City.

36:38.670 --> 36:40.830
Yes.

36:40.830 --> 36:43.350
Yes.

36:43.350 --> 36:44.810
What about the rest of you?

36:44.910 --> 36:46.840
Are you going to disobey the order?

36:49.190 --> 36:50.190
Your Excellency.

36:50.620 --> 36:52.020
I heard that Lady Fan Yun

36:52.020 --> 36:53.940
lit the beacon tower without permission.

36:53.940 --> 36:55.020
I'd like to ask

36:55.140 --> 36:57.270
if she will be held accountable for it.

36:57.310 --> 36:58.390
Your Excellency.

36:59.060 --> 37:02.270
Lady Fan Yun hasn't shown up yet.

37:02.620 --> 37:03.500
I wonder

37:03.710 --> 37:05.840
if she is trying to escape punishment.

37:06.500 --> 37:07.960
Lighting the beacon tower

37:08.420 --> 37:09.750
was my doing.

37:09.750 --> 37:12.010
It has nothing to do with His Excellency.

37:27.060 --> 37:28.060
Your Excellency,

37:29.870 --> 37:31.020
I can resign,

37:31.390 --> 37:32.270
but not now.

37:33.060 --> 37:34.020
I know

37:34.100 --> 37:35.190
that all the ministers

37:35.190 --> 37:36.590
may have some objections

37:36.750 --> 37:38.710
to women becoming officials.

37:39.140 --> 37:40.940
But since I have become a female official,

37:40.940 --> 37:43.350
I want to take this responsibility
seriously.

37:43.350 --> 37:44.100
Your Excellency,

37:44.100 --> 37:45.100
I request

37:45.100 --> 37:46.940
that before the plague in Yong City
is controlled,

37:46.940 --> 37:47.860
you allow me

37:48.310 --> 37:49.540
to make amends for my mistakes

37:49.540 --> 37:50.830
and continue to do good deeds
for the people.

37:50.830 --> 37:53.790
Make amends for your mistakes
and do good deeds for the people?

37:53.790 --> 37:55.500
I'm afraid
you won't be able to make amends,

37:55.500 --> 37:57.100
and your crime will be aggravated.

37:57.100 --> 37:58.100
Your Excellency.

37:58.140 --> 37:58.910
Enough.

38:00.000 --> 38:01.460
I already know about this.

38:02.350 --> 38:04.140
Lord Jiang has reported to me

38:04.830 --> 38:06.500
and recommended Lady Fan Yun.

38:07.230 --> 38:08.360
The top priority now

38:08.620 --> 38:10.540
is to control the plague in Yong City.

38:10.540 --> 38:11.750
I promise you

38:11.750 --> 38:13.140
that when the plague subsides

38:13.140 --> 38:15.340
and Lady Fan Yun returns from Yong City,

38:15.350 --> 38:16.190
this matter

38:16.190 --> 38:18.350
will definitely be handled
according to the law.

38:18.350 --> 38:19.350
Your Excellency.

38:19.870 --> 38:21.790
Although we really want
to accomplish this task,

38:21.790 --> 38:22.830
we

38:24.310 --> 38:25.900
are not capable enough.

38:26.350 --> 38:27.680
What's the difficulty?

38:28.390 --> 38:29.710
The Nine Cities is so big.

38:29.710 --> 38:30.980
Collecting so much sweet wormwood

38:30.980 --> 38:32.190
in such a short time—

38:32.710 --> 38:34.940
aren't you making it too difficult for us?

38:34.940 --> 38:35.790
Your Excellency,

38:35.790 --> 38:36.940
you once said

38:36.940 --> 38:37.830
you wouldn't

38:37.830 --> 38:39.290
rely on us for this matter.

38:39.500 --> 38:41.230
But now you're assigning us the task.

38:41.230 --> 38:41.760
Isn't...

38:42.020 --> 38:43.760
Isn't this going back on your word?

38:43.760 --> 38:45.290
Yong City is in trouble now.

38:45.390 --> 38:46.940
The Nine Cities being united

38:46.940 --> 38:48.140
is what we should do.

38:48.620 --> 38:49.980
I'm afraid I can't do this.

38:49.980 --> 38:51.540
Please withdraw your order,
Your Excellency.

38:51.540 --> 38:52.180
You...

38:53.580 --> 38:55.580
Your Excellency, Your Excellency.

38:56.390 --> 38:57.230
Your Excellency,

38:57.230 --> 38:59.290
Lord Zheng has submitted a memorial.

38:59.750 --> 39:00.540
Read it.

39:01.600 --> 39:03.910
Lord Zheng has gathered
all the sweet wormwood

39:03.910 --> 39:06.030
in Jing City and sent it to Ling'an

39:06.190 --> 39:08.060
to make a modest contribution.

39:08.060 --> 39:10.550
He hopes to alleviate the suffering
of the people in Yong City

39:10.550 --> 39:12.790
and relieve your worries.

39:13.980 --> 39:14.910
Now,

39:15.790 --> 39:17.650
do you have any other objections?

39:18.230 --> 39:19.060
Well...

39:21.750 --> 39:22.620
Ji City

39:22.620 --> 39:25.500
will follow Your Excellency's order.

39:25.670 --> 39:26.630
Wang City

39:26.790 --> 39:29.260
will follow Your Excellency's order.

39:29.540 --> 39:32.660
We will fulfill our mission.

39:40.190 --> 39:40.940
Cover it tightly.

39:40.940 --> 39:42.230
Don't let it fall out.

39:48.710 --> 39:49.710
Miss Wei.

39:51.870 --> 39:52.800
What do you mean?

39:52.870 --> 39:54.620
It's for you to take with you on the road.

39:54.620 --> 39:55.620
Everyone has one.

39:56.910 --> 39:58.750
But yours is the most special.

39:59.270 --> 40:00.190
I can see that.

40:00.190 --> 40:00.670
Here.

40:00.670 --> 40:01.600
Thank you, Miss.

40:03.370 --> 40:04.580
But Miss Wei,

40:04.670 --> 40:06.140
Yong City has always been dry
with little rain,

40:06.140 --> 40:07.390
especially at this time of year.

40:07.390 --> 40:08.710
We'd better simplify our belongings

40:08.710 --> 40:09.980
and march fast.

40:10.230 --> 40:12.270
I specially wove it
using Lanshan vines from Gao City.

40:12.270 --> 40:13.270
It's very light.

40:13.270 --> 40:14.160
Try it if you don't believe me.

40:14.160 --> 40:14.720
I...

40:19.830 --> 40:22.200
Being on the road
is not like being at home.

40:22.310 --> 40:24.640
Be prepared for anything, just in case.

40:25.100 --> 40:26.910
I don't know what you might run into,

40:26.910 --> 40:28.890
so I prepared this for you.

40:41.250 --> 40:43.940
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

40:43.970 --> 40:45.180
♪ Over the whole town ♪

40:45.210 --> 40:47.710
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

40:47.850 --> 40:51.420
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

40:54.100 --> 40:56.570
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

40:56.600 --> 40:57.960
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

40:57.980 --> 41:00.870
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

41:00.970 --> 41:04.440
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

41:03.100 --> 41:04.430
Why are you ignoring me?

41:05.850 --> 41:09.190
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

41:09.250 --> 41:12.280
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪

41:10.100 --> 41:11.830
The strap is too tight.

41:11.830 --> 41:12.910
I'll loosen it for you.

41:12.300 --> 41:14.300
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

41:14.320 --> 41:17.440
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

41:17.470 --> 41:19.470
♪ We'll ride upstream and downs ♪

41:19.490 --> 41:21.920
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

41:20.670 --> 41:21.350
Thank you.

41:22.170 --> 41:25.180
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

41:22.310 --> 41:23.140
Well...

41:24.750 --> 41:25.620
I'm leaving.

41:25.310 --> 41:30.110
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

41:26.500 --> 41:27.830
Don't forget to miss me.

41:29.830 --> 41:30.870
Set off immediately!

41:30.140 --> 41:32.140
♪ Every dark night fades at last ♪

41:32.170 --> 41:34.690
♪ When fate resides within our sight ♪

41:34.800 --> 41:39.480
♪ Gazing toward each other's
distant light ♪

41:39.590 --> 41:43.010
♪ Why would heaven and earth
seek to be with you to save us ♪

41:43.040 --> 41:46.140
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

42:15.110 --> 42:23.850
[Ling'an City]

42:15.540 --> 42:17.710
The Governor is leaving the city

42:17.710 --> 42:19.920
for Yong City

42:20.310 --> 42:23.190
to eliminate the epidemic!

42:24.350 --> 42:27.060
The Governor is leaving the city

42:27.060 --> 42:29.580
for Yong City

42:29.650 --> 42:32.520
to eliminate the epidemic!

42:38.540 --> 42:39.670
Your Excellency.

42:39.800 --> 42:41.350
Do we have to be so flashy

42:41.380 --> 42:42.930
leaving the city this time?

42:43.270 --> 42:45.270
Why do we have to make such a big fuss?

42:46.710 --> 42:48.190
Once we leave Ling'an City,

42:48.190 --> 42:50.460
there might be dangerous forces
staring at us.

42:50.460 --> 42:51.750
Masters from all over the land

42:51.750 --> 42:53.750
have a duty to protect the Governor.

42:53.870 --> 42:55.070
So at a time like this,

42:55.240 --> 42:56.670
the bigger the fuss we make,

42:56.670 --> 42:57.800
the safer we will be.

43:04.100 --> 43:04.780
Gao Ran!

43:05.490 --> 43:06.870
Once we pass the Ling'an checkpoint,

43:06.870 --> 43:08.400
move forward at full speed.

43:08.420 --> 43:09.120
Yes.

43:37.270 --> 43:37.940
Boss.

43:40.100 --> 43:40.910
You're back?

43:41.230 --> 43:42.160
Are you alright?

43:42.420 --> 43:43.270
We're fine.

43:43.890 --> 43:44.970
These bandits

43:45.060 --> 43:47.100
were just after the sweet wormwood
we were escorting.

43:47.100 --> 43:49.500
They didn't want to fight us
for real at all.

43:50.620 --> 43:52.750
Did you get a clear look at their faces?

43:53.020 --> 43:53.940
It was too dark.

43:54.390 --> 43:55.850
I didn't see them clearly.

43:56.100 --> 43:57.100
It's just that...

43:58.230 --> 43:59.350
Go ahead.

44:00.190 --> 44:01.680
It's just that their moves

44:02.020 --> 44:03.220
were a bit like yours.

44:06.020 --> 44:07.230
In other words,

44:08.230 --> 44:10.360
they really work for the Zheng family.

44:11.420 --> 44:13.310
So Miss Fan Yun's trip this time

44:14.270 --> 44:15.910
is likely to be fraught with danger.
